snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner Swap VS 2 Hunters
snippet.description:
This was crazy intense. Manhunt, but with a twist.

This video, I teamed up with a Manhunt NOOB, Dr Donut, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

Follow my socials:
➽ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
➽ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
➽ Snapchat - @dreampublic


In this challenge Dr Donut and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.

This is one of my first ever collabs of this type, if you'd like to see more, like the video!

This was played on Minecraft 1.21.8, and is a custom coded challenge. There were a few bugs that we plan to iron out before we try something like this again!

200,000 likes for me to try this challenge with someone else!

snippet.description:
Laxmi Aarti | Om Jai Laxmi Mata | Lakshmi Mata Ki Aarti | Laxmi Mata Aarti | Diwali | Dhanteras

🌸 Om Jai Laxmi Mata 🌸
Listen to this divine Lakshmi Mata Ki Aarti and invite prosperity, peace, and positivity into your home this Diwali and Dhanteras.
Chant with devotion and experience the blessings of Goddess Mahalaxmi, the goddess of wealth and fortune.

✨ Aarti Lyrics (in Hindi):
ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता, मैया जय लक्ष्मी माता।
तुमको निशदिन सेवत, हरि विष्णु विधाता॥

🕯️ Perfect for:

Dhanteras Puja
Diwali Laxmi Pujan
Friday Aarti
Daily Evening Bhakti

Title :- Om Jai Lakshmi Mata 
Singer :- Varsha Shrivastava
Music :- Vijay Nanda
Video :- SMP Studio

Lyrics

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता, मैया जय लक्ष्मी माता।
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Maiya Jai Lakshmi Mata.

तुमको निशिदिन सेवत, हरि विष्णु विधाता॥
Tumko Nishidin Sevat, Hari Vishnu Vidhata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

उमा, रमा, ब्रह्माणी, तुम ही जग-माता।
Uma, Rama, Brahmani, Tum Hi Jag-Mata.

सूर्य-चंद्रमा ध्यावत, नारद ऋषि गाता॥
Surya-Chandrama Dhyavat, Narad Rishi Gata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

दुर्गा रुप निरंजनी, सुख सम्पत्ति दाता।
Durga Roop Niranjani, Sukh Sampatti Data.

जो कोई तुमको ध्यावत, ऋद्धि-सिद्धि धन पाता॥
Jo Koi Tumko Dhyavat, Riddhi-Siddhi Dhan Pata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

तुम पाताल-निवासिनि, तुम ही शुभदाता।
Tum Patal-Nivasini, Tum Hi Shubhdata.

कर्म-प्रभाव-प्रकाशिनी, भवनिधि की त्राता॥
Karm-Prabhav-Prakashini, Bhavanidhi Ki Trata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

जिस घर में तुम रहतीं, सब सद्गुण आता।
Jis Ghar Mein Tum Rahti, Sab Sadgun Aata.

सब सम्भव हो जाता, मन नहीं घबराता॥
Sab Sambhav Ho Jata, Man Nahi Ghabrata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

तुम बिन यज्ञ न होते, वस्त्र न कोई पाता।
Tum Bin Yagya Na Hote, Vastra Na Koi Pata.

खान-पान का वैभव, सब तुमसे आता॥
Khan-Pan Ka Vaibhav, Sab Tumse Aata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

शुभ-गुण मंदिर सुंदर, क्षीरोदधि-जाता।
Shubh-Gun Mandir Sundar, Kshirodadhi-Jata.

रत्न चतुर्दश तुम बिन, कोई नहीं पाता॥
Ratna Chaturdash Tum Bin, Koi Nahi Pata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

महालक्ष्मीजी की आरती, जो कोई जन गाता।
Mahalakshmi Ji Ki Aarti, Jo Koi Jan Gata.

उर आनन्द समाता, पाप उतर जाता॥
Ur Anand Samata, Paap Utar Jata.

ओम जय लक्ष्मी माता॥
Om Jai Lakshmi Mata.

snippet.title: Ali Amran feat Melissa Sekhi
snippet.description:
Nouveau single tiré de mon nouvel album à venir :  "Gar Yigenni d tmurt"

"À travers des paroles sobres et poignantes, Ali Amran aborde la fuite des cerveaux et la douleur des générations contraintes de s’exiler pour construire leur avenir. Fidèle à son style mêlant poésie et lucidité, il livre une réflexion profonde sur la condition de la jeunesse et l’absence d’espoir dans certaines régions du pays". Sarali Bellamine (commentaire sur Facebook)

Dihin axir

Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
ṛuḥ a mmi, dihin axir
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-is i ddunit
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir

Ziɣ mačči dayen isehlen
tura mi d-tewweḍ rrekba
xas ẓriɣ dayen ilaqen
ɣer daxel, ččiɣ tiyita
‘g yiwwas ad tṛuḥeḍ dayen
lḥess-ik ur s-selleɣ ara
ma siwleɣ w'ara d-yerren
w'ara d-yinin : aql-i da !

Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
ṛuḥ a mmi dihin axir
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-is i ddunit
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir

'G wasmi telliḍ d ameẓyan
nekki d aḥebbeṛ fell-ak
d ac'ara k-d-aǧwen wussan
m' ara tekfuḍ leqraya-k
tamurt ur tesɛi laman
amek ad tḍemneḍ azekka-k?
asigna s-tekkat yettban

wagi d-yuɣen d asekkak

Abrid n lehna 'd talwit
A lbaz areqman
ṛuḥ a mmi dihin axir
ẓwer kan
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-is i ddunit
abrid ad k-iban
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir
a w’ufan

I yessers deg-neɣ zzman
I nɛebba mebla lebɣi
rwin ula d iḥulfan
ger tasa ‘d wul, d imenɣi
nefṛeḥ nessufeɣ igwerdan
d lxir i sen-nettmenni
ǧǧan-d ilem yesseḥzan
nṛebba-ten i lbeṛṛani

ṛuḥ a mmi dihin axir
ad s-tafeḍ ixef-isi ddunit
ma trebḥeḍ, ad ɣ-d-terreḍ lxir
